data.description: This home which offers 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths is ready for new owners. Sitting on a deep lot with a large backyard and above ground pool and deck, it is perfect for entertaining in the warmer months. A partially finished attic makes great space for extra storage or an office. The single stall detached garage was converted to an office/lounge, but could also be opened back up with an overhead garage door for a vehicle. Brand new hot water tank. Located in Whitesboro School District and close to all local amenities this property is in a great location.
